results.title: Wedding Cake Topper Silhouette Couple Mr & Mrs Personalized with Last Name, Acrylic Cake Topper [CT3b]
results.description:
This Silhouette Couple, Mr & Mrs Personalized with Last Name, offers a unique way of expressing your love on your special day. This topper is laser cut from 1/8" thick food safe acrylic and sized perfectly to fit a 6" top tier cake. It measures is 5.5" tall by 4" wide (size will vary with Last Name).  The two non-removable 1.75" cake stakes are not included in the over-all height. It is very lightweight yet sturdy, so it will not sink into your cake. 

PLEASE NOTE:  Names with SIX (6) to TEN (10) letters work best. If your name has LESS THAN SIX (6) letters, choose from the 3rd picture above, on how you would like your name arranged, and NOTE it on your order.

~~ TO ORDER ~~
1. Please select a COLOR from the drop down list.
2. In the Note to seller box, please note the following:
    ~ LAST NAME 
    ~ DATE needed by

Processing time on cake toppers is currently 5-7 BUSINESS days, but may be longer during the busy wedding season.  This is the time it takes for us to create your order, and then your topper is wrapped and packaged securely and safely for shipping, and shipped via USPS First Class Mail to all United States destinations, which usually takes 2-5 business days to reach you once shipped.  Upgraded faster shipping is available at checkout.  We also ship USPS First Class International Mail to all International addresses and shipping time will per country.

~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ 
ADD a "KEEPSAKE" Option!
~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ 
Add a KEEPSAKE display option by adding Removable Spikes and Display Base to any Cake Topper by clicking on this here:
https://www.etsy.com/listing/204463106/add-a-keepsake-display-option-by-adding?ref=shop_home_active_1vary 

TrueloveAffair also offers custom designs based on an image or artwork that you provide. If you have a custom design in mind, send it to us in a message and we will be happy to work with you to create a topper custom tailored to you!  

~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~
RUSH ORDERS:
~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~ ~	
We personally produce all of our toppers so we are able to offer RUSH ORDERS, if you order at least 2 days before your event and if we are shipping to an address in the Continental United States.  Use the link below to guarantee that your order goes to the front of the production line:

https://www.etsy.com/listing/191681445/rush-production-time-on-your-order-rush?ref=shop_home_feat_3

We can also quote you pricing for overnight, or second day shipping.

Thank you so much for visiting our TrueloveAffair shop!  Please message me with any questions or special requests!
